## Weather APIs
# OpenWeatherMap key for live weather endpoints and agri weather rules.
WEATHER_API_KEY=
# Optional city override for weather lookups.
OWM_CITY=Jaipur

## CORS
# Comma-separated origins. Keep '*' only for local/dev testing.
# Example:
# ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://greenblock.anupmazumdar.me,http://localhost:5173
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=*

## Serial bridge settings (greenblock-backend/serial_bridge.py)
SERIAL_PORT=/dev/ttyACM0
BAUD_RATE=9600
BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8000
RETRY_DELAY=5
POST_TIMEOUT=5
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
